document_notes.text:
This update for gnutls fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-5981: Fixed timing side-channel inside RSA-PSK key exchange (bsc#1217277).

notes.text: A vulnerability was found that the response times to malformed ciphertexts in RSA-PSK ClientKeyExchange differ from response times of ciphertexts with correct PKCS#1 v1.5 padding.
